{"tid":2310960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國會通過新法　勒令退市　度身訂造　有冇中共人士、中共章程","createTime":"2020-12-03T16:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T16:41:56.000Z","uid":261647,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"29862d26570c6fc41a0e5774463e400156ae82a0","tid":2310960,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:00:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Buddi/posts/10157926415877934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBuddi%2Fposts%2F10157926415877934&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=97b410fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Buddi/posts/10157926415877934</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：嚴昌浩<br />\n<br />\n真係可喜可賀.<br />\n<br />\nS.945 Holding Foreign Companies Accountable Act 喺今年5月20日已經係參議院一致通過.<br />\n<br />\nS.945 Holding Foreign Companies Accountable Act 喺今日12月2日已經係眾議院又係一致通過.<br />\n<br />\n法案好簡單. 就係所有外國公司必須聘用美國有關當局核准合資格會計師核數，並將有關數薄呈交有關當局（即係SEC）. 否則勒令退市. （以前係無掩雞籠，中國核數師核完嘅數簿經過潤飾，照樣係美國上市，袋袋平安）.<br />\n<br />\n勁抽嘅地方係，此法案係為咗中國共產黨度身訂造.<br />\n<br />\n因為最後嘅 Section 3 Additional Disclosure 開宗明義要公司透露有無外國持股，包括有無共產黨人士係董事局及公司有冇共產黨黨章之類.<br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<br />\n(4) the name of each official of the Chinese Communist Party who is a member of the board of directors of - (A) the issuer; or (B) the operating entity with respect to the issuer; and<br />\n<br />\n(5) whether the articles of incorporation of the issuer (or equivalent organizing document) contains any charter of the Chinese Communist Party, including the text of any such charter.<br />\n<br />\n問你死未.<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/945\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fsenate-bill%2F945&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=4b57dff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/945</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kennedy.senate.gov/public/press-releases?ID=78FE3BCA-EA31-4036-B2AA-A5F8F28B3160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kennedy.senate.gov%2Fpublic%2Fpress-releases%3FID%3D78FE3BCA-EA31-4036-B2AA-A5F8F28B3160&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=a3a2879a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kennedy.senate.gov/public/press-releases?ID=78FE3BCA-EA31-4036-B2AA-A5F8F28B3160</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sX2Aaei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsX2Aaei.jpg&h=9898b8db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YsfFmk0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYsfFmk0.jpg&h=5dad49cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b234460df20c538de860b7d8569b88d455bcd8ed","tid":2310960,"uid":12599,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:03:59.000Z","msg":"即係迫中國d企業同中共割蓆或者執包袱走人"},{"pid":"4fac130f699e4533b7c54e93d86cd582db1d0162","tid":2310960,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b234460df20c538de860b7d8569b88d455bcd8ed","tid":2310960,"uid":12599,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:03:59.000Z","msg":"即係迫中國d企業同中共割蓆或者執包袱走人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"你都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全部都係國企 點會割蓆"},{"pid":"ad507d19206349f6721adf58895de36a756e7366","tid":2310960,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:06:10.000Z","msg":"唔合規 退市！"},{"pid":"d2e7711077ff25c8659e8478cad632089eb47f07","tid":2310960,"uid":39488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"民營企業又怎會和偉大光明正確的共產黨割蓆呢!咱們回家做韮菜去!"},{"pid":"73a92b3d1b0c1b056660182b985ca9d7ee8f7d8d","tid":2310960,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"迫佢哋返晒香港上市<br />\n之前美國公司cap埋呢浸水就正式落刀殺香港"},{"